{
  "stem": "19596.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And [SIGHS] my father had made contact with the Costa Rican consul.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The Costa Rican consul in Berlin were issuing visas-- not only visas, nationalities and passports as well for money, for big money.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But he issued too many, you see?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then all of a sudden, when we were ready to go to Costa Rica with a visa and a passport, he was arrested.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he had the visa and passport?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was trying to get the Jews out, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But-- for money, naturally.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, you know, the whole thing collapsed, so we couldn't go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Where German Jews had opportunity to go, because they had German passport with a J on it-- Jude.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But still, countries like South America gave those passports visas, where England didn't either, because they were afraid-- they were afraid that the-- there was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, you couldn't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was not possibility.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, have I got memory of Kristallnacht?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sure I did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "On the 9th of November, 1938, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] in the nighttime, we heard terrible noises and screaming of people all over Berlin.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They broke all the windows.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What I saw is a red sky of about 20 synagogues being burned, and screaming people, and-- and then-- and brownshirts running through the streets, arresting Jews and hitting Jews, and dragging them out, and plundering, and--",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--trucks-- trucks-- on trucks, and away to Sachsenhausen.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In bed.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mm-hmm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got a telephone call from Betar to get outside immediately, and I'll be picked up with a truck.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the truck was a Betar truck to-- to-- to collect the youth, because we had to run in the shuls [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] [SOBBING] to save the torot.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
